    "body": "We don't really want to add this in go-ethereum. A full function signature parser would be a lot of code, and might not always match the full Solidity feature set.\r\n\r\nIf you want this feature, and you are willing to implement it, I think it could be a good candidate for a stand-alone Go package. 'selector string' to 'ABI definition' transformation can be implemented without the rest of package abi. We could even put a reference to this package in the docs of our package abi. \r\n\r\n",
